      "message": "... and to be clear: If we ever want something like this, it can be added back with a more well-defined behavior. I\u0027m increasingly leaning towards features like this existing only in the C++ API (not as part of the language). For example: Supplying a sentinel value for a uniform when you call makeShader, that binds the uniform to a marked matrix. That stops the SkSL language spec (which may soon be long-lived) from dictating and necessitating Skia features that become hard to maintain or remove.",
